### PAT-WEBVIEW ###

A lightweight WebKitGTK-based viewer for PAT Winlink's web interface.
Replaces the Firefox ICE webapp with a clean, native-feeling window.

### FEATURES ###

- Minimal, native GTK window (no browser chrome)
- Keyboard shortcuts: F5/Ctrl+R (refresh), Ctrl+Q (quit), F11 (fullscreen)
- External links open in default browser
- Friendly error page if PAT service is not running
- Desktop actions for restart and save config

### INSTRUCTIONS ###

1) Move PAT-WEBVIEW directory into USER Module directory.

2) Move 21_PAT-WEBVIEW.sh into USER Module directory.
   - Up one level from the PAT-WEBVIEW directory

Notes:
- Runs after 20_PAT.sh (the core PAT module)
- Replaces the ICE webapp launcher
- To deactivate, move script back into PAT-WEBVIEW directory
